<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="excitement-n">excitement <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪk'saɪtmənt/    美 /ɪk'saɪtmənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>兴奋；激动：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When their wish came true they cheered <strong>in excitement</strong>.
梦想实现了，他们激动得欢呼起来。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[正式用语] 令人兴奋 / 激动的事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The visiting circus was an excitement to every child in town. 
马戏团的到来使镇上的每个孩子都很兴奋。</p></div></div>